thread.title_full: BRIEF-BIMobject moves to Skanska's new building studio in Malmö | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-BIMobject moves to Skanska's new building studio in Malmö
text:
Oct 8 BIMobject AB :
* BIMobject has signed Skanska's lease to move to STUDIO in Malmö after it is completed
* BIMobject will therefore relocate its headquarters in the autumn of 2016 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
